### Get all Packages
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/packages/

### Get single package (by ID)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/packages/1

### Create new package
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/packages
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Safekitchen plus",
  "components": ["Smart Stove Sensor", "Voice Assistant", "Auto Shutoff Device"],
  "accessibility": 9,
  "steps": [
    "Install stove sensor",
    "Connect to wifi",
    "Test voice commands"
  ]
}

### Get package that does not exist (404 test)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/packages/99999

### Create package with invalid accessibility (test validation)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/packages
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test Package",
  "components": ["Test Component"],
  "accessibility": 15,
  "steps": ["Test step"]
}